{"id":"21a184faacda0879541e5bc0e66495a837db4b79108c798c0f4831aa5632f2a2","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:0","text":"Light Filters（灯光滤镜）用于操控 lighting results（照明结果）。在真实拍摄中，这通常通过 stencils（遮片）和 gels（滤色片）来改变镜头中光的颜色、质感和光量。RenderMan 的 light filters 是一种强大而灵活的方式，可在场景照明中完成同样的工作，甚至做得更多。"}
{"id":"8fd14452d9d71efa7bf6fb146f261fb8e8ad4ddfd60376c6a92dd65d6a3d8a85","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:1","text":"Create Light Filters（创建灯光滤镜）"}
{"id":"cf611a56082831298bf2e446a7619ba842afd737ecb9d26d663514170bd1a158","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:2","text":"要为灯光添加 light filter（灯光滤镜），先从 Add 菜单创建一个 light filter："}
{"id":"b64231dacb9ba3aa56e576d5be73023a12ffba0ec2cfd07976ae458460187477","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:3","text":"接下来，选择想要添加滤镜的灯光，并查看 object properties panel（对象属性面板）。你应该会看到 Light Filters 面板。"}
{"id":"c96b4f3364d1870ec0f854ce9f664eb79c42540dedc1a9faf295dcaec6ee4191","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:4","text":"点击"}
{"id":"5deff5fa9700fa8e2901a9a9db757d0b37b9f08f91a98d47afc9b0e478e1ef00","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:5","text":"以添加新条目，然后选择要链接的 light filter object（灯光滤镜对象）。"}
{"id":"5753ea3780f34ad1295fb9957f1575e7e7578aa0e891d89524c26ad6f504cb1d","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:6","text":"Shortcut（快捷方式）"}
{"id":"515fd5d991c34f4e868d166955800485ffdbd9028414da62f0674c1003f52d71","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:7","text":"也可以使用 object context menu（对象上下文菜单）中的快捷方式。选择想要过滤的灯光，并从 Attach New Light Filter 菜单中选择要添加的 light filter。新的 light filter 会自动添加到 light filters 列表中。"}
{"id":"fe2203b732c02bb2d8863d8729457eb7d078cbf94a6b13123afe7aa306f0cfcf","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:8","text":"Light Filter Types（灯光滤镜类型）"}
{"id":"af4e316a2f1cd2f3ecba88df0269ec8be6ebcce40dc24de6ef76376bbb568fd5","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:9","text":"有关参数的详细信息，请跟随每种 light filter type（灯光滤镜类型）的链接。"}
{"id":"217d39972aa9a988c2db9dcc6ff6c9936eb9169e0fc1d8e59d013d00caa4f9a0","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:10","text":"PxrBarnLightFilter"}
{"id":"522b0133194a3ff5dfb87e1325c96268a22d03f81fb5fb0a90877a5060a16da9","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:11","text":"PxrBlockerLightFilter"}
{"id":"390bebab7703ade2a7b8fcca564e95b70dea0f44c72eb16f01b7fe659186bb5a","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:12","text":"PxrCookieLightFilter"}
{"id":"f6ebc84434da7bfca37310080de62dbe8c2f58ad939addad673bee1a389f6f6e","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:13","text":"PxrGoboLightFilter"}
{"id":"69520493bbe1cafac9be955f3e2af6c5d9f04c4ea151c105aec2bf78a6f5456b","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:14","text":"PxrIntMultLightFilter"}
{"id":"92efbdc93580b3e902de4fce226991d965b198d47d61e2c8e1dc469a4b90a1b0","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:15","text":"PxrRampLightFilter"}
{"id":"ae1554c0e5c6428019fb763583b92b5bab804cd86b0201005ad86fcd4dc04115","item_id":"d1d3cf8475:16","text":"PxrRodLightFilter"}
